<bibRefCitation id="71412AFFFFA6FFD8B3FF516CFBA6F8E6" author="Danzig, E. M. &amp; Gavrilov-Zimin, I. A." box="[661,1034,1806,1833]" pageId="41" pageNumber="42" refId="ref87819" refString="Danzig, E. M. &amp; Gavrilov-Zimin, I. A. (2015) Palaearctic mealybugs (Homoptera: Coccinea: Pseudococcidae). Part 2: Subfamily Pseudococcinae. Russian Academy of Sciences, Zoological Institute, St. Petersburg, 619 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.31610 / zsr / 2015.24.2.236" type="book" year="2015">Danzig &amp; Gavrilov-Zimin (2015)</bibRefCitation>
differed from the Iranian specimens by lacking translucent pores on the hind femur and tibia.
</paragraph>
